@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

state "Off" as Off
state "Alarm Set" as AlarmSet
state "Ringing" as Ringing

[*] --> Off

Off --> [*]

Off --> AlarmSet : set alarm time
AlarmSet --> Ringing : current time matches alarm time
Ringing --> AlarmSet : turn off alarm

AlarmSet --> AlarmSet : current time does not match alarm time
Ringing --> Ringing : alarm is still ringing
@enduml
